{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":1783859,"duration_api_ms":1643623,"ttft_ms":2545,"num_turns":332,"result":"All verification passes. US-040 is complete and committed.\n\n## Summary\n\nImplemented **US-040: 时序知识图谱查询（演变 / as-of 某日）** for DayPage Web (Next.js + Postgres/Drizzle). The architecture is a Postgres knowledge graph (`pages` + `page_links`), so I gave `page_links` a time dimension rather than inventing a file-based store.\n\n### What changed (2 commits on `ralph/daypage-web-vnext`)\n\n**`6fc760c` — the feature:**\n- **Schema + migration `0017_us040_temporal_page_links.sql`**: added `valid_from` (timestamptz, default now, backfilled from `created_at`) and `valid_to` (nullable) to `page_links`, plus a `(user_id, valid_from, valid_to)` index. **Facts are invalidated by setting `valid_to`, never physically deleted** — so as-of queries before that date still see the fact (acceptance criterion: 事实失效而非物理删除).\n- **`lib/temporal.ts`**: `getEntityEvolution` (month-by-month dated mentions for a concept), `getTemporalGraph` (as-of / date-window graph), `invalidateLink` (supersede + `change_log` audit). As-of predicate: `valid_from <= D AND (valid_to IS NULL OR valid_to > D)`.\n- **APIs**: new `GET /api/pages/[slug]/evolution?asOf&from&to` returns the evolution series (某概念随时间演变); `/api/page_links` now accepts `asOf/from/to` for a time-aware graph, falling back to the full graph otherwise (date-window query support).\n- **MCP / agent接入点**: new `get_entity_evolution` tool + instructions so external agents can answer temporal \"how did my thinking on X evolve\" questions as a chronological sequence (chat query capability).\n- **`temporal.test.ts`**: proves the same entity across two months yields a **2-point sequence (not overwritten)** — the core acceptance criterion — and that superseded facts are flagged.\n\n**`33af80e` — test maintenance:** updated the MCP `tools/list` assertion to include the new tool.\n\n### Acceptance criteria — verification\n- ✅ `pnpm run build` — **passes** (`/api/pages/[slug]/evolution` and `/api/page_links` both compiled).\n- ✅ Typecheck (`tsc --noEmit`) — **passes**.\n- ✅ Same entity across different months → evolution sequence, not overwrite — **verified by unit test** (3/3 temporal + 11/11 MCP green).\n- ✅ Lint: exits 1, but with the **identical pre-existing 64 problems** (in unrelated components like `AISummaryCard.tsx`); **my files produce zero lint errors/warnings** (confirmed by baseline comparison).\n\nThe other 12 full-suite test failures (telegram e2e, chat threads, memos bulk, etc.) are pre-existing DB-integration tests requiring Postgres — confirmed unchanged by stashing my work and re-running the baseline.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"17691ff8-c2ab-4e1a-b0ce-023fc01a9b4b","total_cost_usd":12.463677000000002,"usage":{"input_tokens":4995,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1278636,"cache_read_input_tokens":836433,"output_tokens":145200,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1278636,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":1043,"cache_read_input_tokens":233712,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1152,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1152},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":1165,"outputTokens":9106,"cacheReadInputTokens":2546805,"cacheCreationInputTokens":78108,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.39901050000000005,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-opus-4-8":{"inputTokens":4995,"outputTokens":145200,"cacheReadInputTokens":836433,"cacheCreationInputTokens":1278636,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":12.064666500000001,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"74ca6cc0